1
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,180
=My Name is Zhao Chuxi=

2
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:05,100
=Episode 30=

3
00:01:05,620 --> 00:01:09,670
I won't beg for your forgiveness now.

4
00:01:10,430 --> 00:01:13,060
But Zhao Chuxi,

5
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:17,230
I implore you to spare Zhang's Group.

6
00:01:17,870 --> 00:01:20,700
It's the work of my entire life.

7
00:01:22,340 --> 00:01:23,420
Zhao Chuxi,

8
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:25,590
I'm begging you.

9
00:01:27,260 --> 00:01:29,620
This is my final request.

10
00:01:30,540 --> 00:01:33,030
Please save Zhang's Group.

11
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:35,080
No matter what happens after this,

12
00:01:35,670 --> 00:01:38,420
I can give you anything you want.

13
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:42,950
I'll cooperate with whatever you decide.

14
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:53,590
I promise you.

15
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,180
What?

16
00:01:57,180 --> 00:01:58,380
I promise you.

17
00:01:58,380 --> 00:02:00,230
Are you serious about this?

18
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:01,150
Yes, I am.

19
00:02:01,670 --> 00:02:04,420
But you have to meet one condition.

20
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:09,260
You took Zhang's Group from my father.

21
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:11,860
You need to issue a statement

22
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:14,740
clearing up everything

23
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:16,470
that happened before

24
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:19,430
and then return my dad's shares.

25
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:20,350
That's all.

26
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:23,430
That's it?

27
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:25,140
Yes, that's all.

28
00:02:26,110 --> 00:02:27,110
Why?

29
00:02:28,310 --> 00:02:29,860
If you understood this,

30
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:31,910
you wouldn't have lost today.

31
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:35,380
Let's go, Qingyi.

32
00:03:06,050 --> 00:03:06,900
Look.

33
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:09,730
(Share Transfer Agreement)
It's the agreement signed by Zhang Shengbai.

34
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,590
I've reviewed it. There are no issues.

35
00:03:12,220 --> 00:03:13,140
You take another look.

36
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:20,440
(Share Distribution Cooperation Agreement)

37
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,500
(Zhang Shengbai)

38
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,740
To be honest,

39
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,590
I've thought about these documents

40
00:03:27,650 --> 00:03:29,730
on my mind again and again.

41
00:03:29,780 --> 00:03:31,390
And now, looking back on them,

42
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:33,420
everything feels so unreal.

43
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,470
We actually made it.

44
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:39,190
Chuxi, I believed in you from the start.

45
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:40,390
I never doubted it.

46
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:43,590
Erpang, Xu Lin,

47
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:44,630
thank you both.

48
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:46,300
Without you two,

49
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:48,390
I wouldn't be here today.

50
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:50,740
No need to thank us.

51
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:53,500
We've seen everything you've done.

52
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:54,910
You deserve this.

53
00:03:58,020 --> 00:04:00,340
(Share Transfer Agreement)

54
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:18,670
I just received some news.

55
00:04:19,780 --> 00:04:20,980
Zhang Shengbai

56
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,270
has passed away.

57
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,740
Son,

58
00:04:41,780 --> 00:04:43,180
are you here?

59
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:45,110
Dad, what's wrong?

60
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,180
It was my fault.

61
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:54,540
I wasn't a good father.

62
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:56,380
Are you willing

63
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,350
to forgive me?

64
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,060
Dad, what's wrong with you?

65
00:05:03,220 --> 00:05:04,180
Son,

66
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:10,150
don't follow my old path again.

67
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,740
Dad, what's wrong with you?

68
00:05:14,860 --> 00:05:16,030
Dad, what's wrong with you?

69
00:05:17,780 --> 00:05:19,150
Dad, what's wrong with you?

70
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:25,790
Are you unwilling to forgive me?

71
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:47,420
Zhang Shengbai

72
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:50,140
has passed away.

73
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:58,910
He left the group's shares and assets

74
00:06:00,780 --> 00:06:02,470
all to Zhao Chuxi.

75
00:06:04,150 --> 00:06:06,030
Why is it always Zhao Chuxi?

76
00:06:09,030 --> 00:06:11,180
I am your biological son.

77
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:15,110
I am your real hope.

78
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:17,590
I am the continuation of your legacy.

79
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:20,470
Zhao Chuxi carries the Zhao family name.

80
00:06:20,780 --> 00:06:22,180
He is not part of the Zhang family.

81
00:06:23,660 --> 00:06:25,180
Have you lost your mind, father?

82
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:30,700
Exactly.

83
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:34,380
My last name isn't Zhang.

84
00:06:35,710 --> 00:06:36,740
My last name is Xu.

85
00:07:03,150 --> 00:07:04,230
The cue rack.

86
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,430
Do you know how to set the balls?

87
00:07:13,420 --> 00:07:15,110
You totally ruined the mood.

88
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:18,900
I'm a bit short on cash lately.

89
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:20,270
Bring 2,000 yuan tomorrow.

90
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,670
I don't have that much money.

91
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:23,420
You don't have that much.

92
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:27,380
If you don't, I'll find a way.

93
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:28,980
Ask your dad.

94
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:41,460
Come in.

95
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:43,580
Shaoqing,

96
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:46,670
what happened to your face?

97
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,860
I need to borrow 2,000 yuan.

98
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:50,590
Bring these people who bullied him

99
00:07:50,590 --> 00:07:52,790
and their parents, too.

100
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,980
Show me exactly

101
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:57,070
how you bullied Xu Shaoqing.

102
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:59,270
We were playing pool at the billiards hall.

103
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:02,060
My friend kicked him

104
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,510
and told him to pick up the ball.

105
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,590
Stop it.

106
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:06,900
My friend kicked him

107
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:08,190
and told him to pick up the ball.

108
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,040
My friend kicked him

109
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,590
and told him to pick up the ball.

110
00:08:10,590 --> 00:08:11,830
He looked a bit weak.

111
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,630
Let me out of here!

112
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:14,550
Open the door!

113
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:15,950
Is anyone there?

114
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:17,230
I'm dying!

115
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:18,420
I'll show you.

116
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:19,830
I'll show you!

117
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:21,020
Dad!

118
00:08:21,340 --> 00:08:22,300
Dad, please help me!

119
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,190
- Someone bullied me.
- The cue rack.

120
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,270
Hurry up, move quickly!

121
00:08:25,530 --> 00:08:27,030
Do you know how to set up the balls?

122
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:28,190
Dad, Dad...

123
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:29,260
I don't have so much money.

124
00:08:29,270 --> 00:08:30,590
If you don't, I'll find a way.

125
00:08:31,030 --> 00:08:32,060
Dad, please save me.

126
00:08:32,660 --> 00:08:34,190
- Dad...
- You don't have money!

127
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,740
If you don't, ask your dad for it.

128
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:37,590
You need to understand,

129
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:39,390
being too kind-hearted

130
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:42,380
is like a sword with no edge.

131
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:45,180
You must know that power and wealth

132
00:08:45,180 --> 00:08:49,260
are the strongest shield and blade.

133
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:51,620
Once you have them,

134
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:54,110
and pursue them relentlessly,

135
00:08:54,110 --> 00:08:57,260
only then can you get what you want.

136
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,230
It doesn't hurt.

137
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:21,550
3,000.

138
00:09:22,350 --> 00:09:23,660
Can we stop this, Mr. Xu?

139
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:24,900
Set it up.

140
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,710
Here, is it set up right?

141
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:31,340
Answer me.

142
00:09:31,540 --> 00:09:32,460
Is it right?

143
00:09:42,350 --> 00:09:43,620
That's enough.

144
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:45,350
That's enough.

145
00:09:52,350 --> 00:09:57,140
So this is how it feels to be on top.

146
00:10:04,460 --> 00:10:06,340
(Calling...)

147
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:53,870
Hello? Shaoqing, what's up?

148
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:54,790
Xiluo,

149
00:10:55,350 --> 00:10:56,270
we need to talk.

150
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:58,550
Talk about what?

151
00:10:59,180 --> 00:11:00,100
What's going on?

152
00:11:00,820 --> 00:11:03,380
Didn't you say we're friends?

153
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:06,110
Isn't it normal for friends to talk?

154
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:08,230
Nothing.

155
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,420
Alright.

156
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:11,380
Where are you?

157
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:12,660
I'll come pick you up.

158
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:18,500
I'll wait for you downstairs at the company.

159
00:11:30,710 --> 00:11:32,900
Hello? Qi Han, what's up?

160
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:35,260
Xu Shaoqing doesn't look good.

161
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:36,470
What's your plan?

162
00:11:38,180 --> 00:11:39,780
So, what are your plans?

163
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:42,230
We've discussed solutions,

164
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:43,700
but failed to reach a consensus.

165
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,350
I just wanted to ask for your thoughts.

166
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:47,860
Qi Han,

167
00:11:49,870 --> 00:11:51,350
I can only tell you one thing.

168
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:52,900
Reality can be harsh.

169
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:55,350
Sometimes, you have to think for yourself.

170
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:58,380
So whatever you decide, I won't stop you.

171
00:11:58,700 --> 00:11:59,620
Go ahead and act on it.

172
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:01,780
But if you're asking me,

173
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:03,020
I can only tell you this.

174
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,980
Even though Xu Shaoqing is strict with me,

175
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,860
and sometimes scolds me for no reason,

176
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,660
he's still my boss.

177
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:14,380
He's the one who recognized my potential.

178
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:16,500
Sometimes,

179
00:12:17,470 --> 00:12:19,380
you have to stay true to your conscience.

180
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:30,500
You already know the answer.

181
00:12:31,700 --> 00:12:33,110
Why call me

182
00:12:33,110 --> 00:12:34,590
to just seek comfort in yourself?

183
00:12:38,660 --> 00:12:39,740
All these years,

184
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:42,110
I've watched you grow up.

185
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,820
You're practically like a son to me.

186
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:46,830
Yes, Mr. Zhang.

187
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:50,260
If it weren't for your support,

188
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:52,500
I'd probably have starved on the streets.

189
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:54,830
So whatever you need, just let me know.

190
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,550
I'll give it my all.

191
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:01,590
I have a son named Xu Shaoqing.

192
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:04,900
He's rather timid in nature.

193
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,350
When it comes to decisions,

194
00:13:06,990 --> 00:13:08,900
he lacks judgment.

195
00:13:09,060 --> 00:13:11,940
But you, you're sharp-minded.

196
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:13,950
You know what should and shouldn't be done.

197
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:18,230
I want you to stay by his side,

198
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:21,070
assist him, and protect him.

199
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:22,590
What do you think?

200
00:13:22,780 --> 00:13:25,380
Mr. Zhang, absolutely no problem.

201
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:26,830
However,

202
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:29,310
I have one request for you.

203
00:13:29,540 --> 00:13:33,070
Never betray him, no matter what.

204
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:34,740
Can you promise me that?

205
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:35,790
Mr. Zhang,

206
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:39,660
you've supported me all these years.

207
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:42,950
I will always remember your kindness.

208
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:44,700
So, regarding your request,

209
00:13:44,860 --> 00:13:46,660
I'll give it my all.

210
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:49,980
I promise to stay by Xu Shaoqing's side

211
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,780
and do everything to assist him.

212
00:13:52,110 --> 00:13:53,260
I will never betray him.

213
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:56,140
Alright, Guan Yue.

214
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:58,310
I trust your promise.

215
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:00,640
- Have some tea.
- Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

216
00:14:01,420 --> 00:14:02,350
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

217
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:23,550
Why are you looking at me like that?

218
00:14:25,350 --> 00:14:26,270
Xu Shaoqing,

219
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:30,140
do you always handle things so harshly?

220
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:32,410
Have you thought about the consequences?

221
00:14:32,420 --> 00:14:34,080
Why would I care about the consequences?

222
00:14:35,700 --> 00:14:37,310
Right now, I feel like

223
00:14:37,990 --> 00:14:40,710
from inside out, I'm completely ruined.

224
00:14:41,350 --> 00:14:43,110
Because of you and Zhao Chuxi,

225
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:46,660
the two of you destroyed me.

226
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:50,950
I can't believe...

227
00:14:51,420 --> 00:14:53,510
I can't believe I did so many foolish things

228
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:55,310
for the so-called love.

229
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,620
Xu Shaoqing,

230
00:14:59,110 --> 00:15:00,190
calm down for a moment.

231
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:03,350
Think about your family.

232
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:04,460
Yes,

233
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:07,070
my family.

234
00:15:08,660 --> 00:15:09,740
My family...

235
00:15:13,350 --> 00:15:15,020
But, but...

236
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:16,620
I...

237
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,980
I don't have a family anymore.

238
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:20,980
I only have

239
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:24,950
a father who wouldn't even share his surname.

240
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:27,350
He's already gone.

241
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:36,590
He never deserved to be my dad.

242
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:40,950
No, no, no.

243
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:44,020
I should thank him.

244
00:15:54,780 --> 00:15:56,740
Xu Shaoqing, why are you looking for me?

245
00:15:57,780 --> 00:15:58,700
I just want to...

246
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,620
Zhao Chuxi!

247
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:01,060
Zhao Chuxi, he wants to kill you.

248
00:16:01,060 --> 00:16:02,670
- Don't listen to him.
- Wait a second.

249
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:07,620
Xu Shaoqing, what are you really up to?

250
00:16:08,660 --> 00:16:09,860
I just want

251
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:13,660
to ask you out for a chat.

252
00:16:13,970 --> 00:16:15,180
- Xu Shaoqing,
- Is that okay?

253
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:17,320
our issues don't involve him.

254
00:16:17,350 --> 00:16:18,900
Zhao Chuxi, let me tell you this.

255
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:20,150
Stay out of this.

256
00:16:20,150 --> 00:16:22,430
Get as far away as you can, got it?

257
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:25,830
Xu Shaoqing, I'm warning you, don't hurt her.

258
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,620
You're warning me?

259
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:30,780
What gives you the right to warn me?

260
00:16:31,420 --> 00:16:32,900
You want me not to hurt Xiluo?

261
00:16:33,510 --> 00:16:34,430
Fine.

262
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:35,620
Are you coming or not?

263
00:16:36,230 --> 00:16:37,690
I'll give you ten seconds to decide.

264
00:16:38,870 --> 00:16:39,790
One.

265
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:41,670
Two.

266
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:43,220
Three.

267
00:16:43,990 --> 00:16:44,910
Four.

268
00:16:45,350 --> 00:16:47,550
- Five.
- I'll go. Send me the address.

269
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,230
The intersection of Baowei Road
and Shunhe Road.

270
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:53,980
Someone will guide you over.

271
00:16:56,540 --> 00:16:57,660
Are you really going?

272
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:58,700
Yes, I'm going.

273
00:16:59,820 --> 00:17:02,350
Since Xu Shaoqing is looking for death,

274
00:17:03,110 --> 00:17:04,430
I'll help him fulfill that wish.

275
00:17:04,430 --> 00:17:05,620
Then I'll go with you.

276
00:17:05,620 --> 00:17:08,550
No need. Mr. Zhou is coming with me.

277
00:17:08,950 --> 00:17:10,270
Relax, I'll handle it.

278
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:35,380
Well, old acquaintances.

279
00:17:35,380 --> 00:17:36,590
How have things been lately?

280
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:39,190
Are you still wearing the same uniform?

281
00:17:39,190 --> 00:17:42,180
The boss isn't treating you well, huh?

282
00:17:43,990 --> 00:17:45,540
Mr. Zhao, get in the car.

283
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:46,620
Let's talk business first.

284
00:17:49,910 --> 00:17:51,350
Mr. Xu only wants him to go alone.

