291
00:18:21,780 --> 00:18:22,700
Is that it?

292
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:23,780
Exactly.

293
00:18:23,780 --> 00:18:24,700
Xu Shaoqing.

294
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:28,380
You know his current situation well, right?

295
00:18:28,620 --> 00:18:30,270
And yet you're still following him.

296
00:18:30,670 --> 00:18:32,620
