301
00:18:45,270 --> 00:18:48,030
If you're willing to listen to me

302
00:18:48,950 --> 00:18:50,070
and cooperate with me,

303
00:18:50,670 --> 00:18:52,380
I can guarantee your safety.

304
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:56,830
If you two stay stubborn,

305
00:18:57,750 --> 00:19:00,070
and insist on sticking with Xu Shaoqing,

306
