310
00:19:40,100 --> 00:19:42,790
Zhao Chuxi, why are you here?

311
00:19:43,230 --> 00:19:44,150
Zhao Chuxi,

312
00:19:44,710 --> 00:19:46,070
you really came.

313
00:19:46,670 --> 00:19:48,860
Seems like you've got some guts after all.

314
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:50,620
You asked me here,

315
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:52,380
