316
00:19:52,710 --> 00:19:54,270
Guts, sure.

317
00:19:55,100 --> 00:19:58,940
But there's nothing for us to discuss.

318
00:19:59,140 --> 00:20:00,460
No, no, no.

319
00:20:01,470 --> 00:20:03,350
We've got plenty to talk about.

320
00:20:03,750 --> 00:20:04,790
For instance,

321
00:20:06,230 --> 00:20:07,620
the matter involving the three of us

322
00:20:07,860 --> 00:20:09,310
should be settled properly.

323
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:10,350
Wait a moment.

324
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:13,830
This is between you and me.

325
00:20:13,990 --> 00:20:15,590
It has nothing to do with her.

326
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:18,750
Zhao Chuxi, don't try

327
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:20,430
