340
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,020
Alright.

341
00:20:53,670 --> 00:20:54,750
I agree.

342
00:20:55,670 --> 00:20:56,590
Come on.

343
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:16,270
Let her go.

344
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:21,790
